{
    "version": 6,
    "bundle": "4AI3COXO3K2OZQLSMHIL5FZUETUOIMY2",
    "type": "story",
    "storyId": "501135524",
    "title": "遊び心とかくれんぼ",
    "enTitle": "Playful Hide and Seek",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "ある日、トレーナー室に向かうと\n机の上に覚えのないメモ用紙があった。",
            "enText": "One day, I noticed there was a note \nleft on my table.",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 89,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "pathId": 367535244760260068,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "『あの場所に行く。\nあんたも暇なら来い』",
            "enText": "\"I'm going to that place. \nTag along if you're free.\"",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 71,
            "voiceIdx": 37,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 136,
                    "pathId": -8533974512231888914
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 136,
                    "pathId": 4144829761897565987
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7208774531510968722,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "……どういうことなのだろう。\n時間もあるので向かいたいところではあるが、\n『あの場所』がどこか、わからない。",
            "enText": "What does she even mean by that… I do \nhave some free time so I'd like to find her \nbut, where do I even start with \"that place\".",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 115,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 11,
                    "pathId": 8476212349382736459
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 11,
                    "pathId": 1038746498900332562
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3520624402984861930,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "こう言うからには、以前一緒に行った場所を\n指しているのだろうか？\nそう考え、記憶を辿る――",
            "enText": "If she said it like that, then it must be \nsomeplace we've visited before. Now, \nin terms of places we've been to…",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 103,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "河川敷で青空を見ている気がする",
                    "enText": "She's got to be cloud watching by the river",
                    "nextBlock": 5
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "きっと屋上で空を眺めているはず",
                    "enText": "She must be gazing at the sky on the roof",
                    "nextBlock": 23
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "前に寄ってみた街のことかな？",
                    "enText": "Maybe she's in that one town we visited?",
                    "nextBlock": 34
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -504871477292590540,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "やっぱりいいな、ここの青空。",
            "enText": "The sky's great as always here.",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 70,
            "voiceIdx": 75,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 195,
                    "pathId": -6191551737286418332
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 212,
                    "pathId": -5678498060406335538
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 164,
                    "pathId": -2905265792015652400
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8008217299012495741,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "すぅ～……はぁー……いい。いい景色だ。",
            "enText": "<i>Huffff～～ Haaaa</i>. Yeah, it's a great scenery.",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 77,
            "voiceIdx": 59,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 195,
                    "pathId": -549388944367178622
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 88,
                    "pathId": 8479701901495556203
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 88,
                    "pathId": 3436861742301787508
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4963197935213601242,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "ふと、彼女が口にしていた言葉を思い出す。\nあの時、河川敷で見た青空は\n不思議と彼女に響いているように見えた――",
            "enText": "Her face suddenly popped into my head. \nIt was when we were by the river and \nsomething about the sky that day \nreally enticed her.",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 116,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "よし、行ってみよう",
                    "enText": "Alright, guess we're heading there",
                    "nextBlock": 8
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 13,
                    "pathId": 5130603174079794635
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 13,
                    "pathId": 9207965182591063318
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 13,
                    "pathId": -6829199216826384365
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2270241256862353517,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "お、来たな。",
            "enText": "<i>Oh</i>, you made it.",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 52,
            "voiceIdx": 4,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "ステゴ！やっぱりここだったんだな",
                    "enText": "I knew you were here Stego!",
                    "nextBlock": 9
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "ステゴ！やっぱりここだったんだね",
                    "enText": "I knew you were here Stego!",
                    "nextBlock": 9
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 173,
                    "pathId": -1820784965561869154
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 119,
                    "pathId": -1805724702811833259
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 143076843869396712,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "ああ。――さ、こっち来いよ。\n草むらにでも座ってのんびりしよう。",
            "enText": "Yeah. Now get over here, come relax on the \ngrass with me.",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 86,
            "voiceIdx": 80,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 119,
                    "pathId": -8890410442076691486
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 97,
                    "pathId": 1228569380669309986
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3723277924014329029,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "そうそう、美味い菓子もあるんだぞ。\n海外の友人からの贈り物でさ。\nここで食おうと思ってたんだ。",
            "enText": "Oh yeah, I've got some sweets too, a gift \nfrom a friend overseas. Thought we could \nenjoy them here.",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 106,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "ここのこと、好きなんだな",
                    "enText": "You really like this spot hey",
                    "nextBlock": 11
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "ここのこと、好きなんだね",
                    "enText": "You really like this spot hey",
                    "nextBlock": 11
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 79,
                    "pathId": -6748885257596902351
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 117,
                    "pathId": 6989958470456754900
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 376334996470150420,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "…………。\n空を見てみろ。",
            "enText": "……… \nTake a gander at the sky.",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 61,
            "voiceIdx": 52,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 195,
                    "pathId": -5930969731286312710
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 72,
                    "pathId": 4695199967078543125
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 72,
                    "pathId": 5507010588983253983
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2774206235940014265,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "空を見上げてみる。そこには広い青空に雲が\n浮かんでいるだけだった。",
            "enText": "I raised my head to gaze at the infinitely \nwide blue sky. A few clouds floated \ngently above us.",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 88,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "えっと……いい青空だな",
                    "enText": "Uhm… It's a wonderful sky",
                    "nextBlock": 13
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "えっと……いい青空だね",
                    "enText": "Uhm… It's a wonderful sky",
                    "nextBlock": 13
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 13,
                    "pathId": 5819514615866575798
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 13,
                    "pathId": 3314945503081552906
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 13,
                    "pathId": -34123228903352449
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7436454612766156277,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "ああ、ただのいい青空だ。ただ――",
            "enText": "Yeah, it's only a nice blue sky… Only ——",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 65,
            "voiceIdx": 47,
            "pathId": 5353342807452710339,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "この日常にある空はどこまでも続いている。\n建物の先にも……川の先にも、\nなんなら国境の先まで。",
            "enText": "This sky we see everyday stretches on \ninfinitely no matter where we go. It \nstretches past buildings… past rivers, \neven all the way over borders.",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "origClipLength": 106,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "pathId": -8039323464015012638,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "そう思うと、なんだかワクワクしてこないか？",
            "enText": "Imagining the sky like that, don't you \nstart to feel a little excited inside?",
            "nextBlock": 16,
            "origClipLength": 72,
            "voiceIdx": 0,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "なんとなくわかる……かも？",
                    "enText": "I think I get what you mean…?",
                    "nextBlock": 16
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7777087750162297733,
            "blockIdx": 15
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "ふっ、無理にわかろうとしなくてもいい。\n私はそう感じてるってだけだからな。",
            "enText": "<i>Hum</i>, it's alright if you don't really get it, \nI'm just narrating my feelings, that's all.",
            "nextBlock": 17,
            "origClipLength": 93,
            "voiceIdx": 37,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 172,
                    "pathId": -7098768573778159755
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 153,
                    "pathId": -163948671760264878
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -30385226275829334,
            "blockIdx": 16
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "……さて、川のそばまで降りよう。\nちょうどいい風も吹いてきたとこだしな。",
            "enText": "…Now then, let's go down to the riverbank. \nThere just so happens to be a nice breeze \ncoming through.",
            "nextBlock": 18,
            "origClipLength": 91,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 108,
                    "pathId": -832530188425148949
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 102,
                    "pathId": -461857064501229787
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1646906933091829893,
            "blockIdx": 17
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "こうして、彼女とお菓子を食べるために\n川の方へと向かうのだった。",
            "enText": "I was led down by Stay Gold to enjoy \nour sweets by the riverside.",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "origClipLength": 86,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 102,
                    "pathId": 2205239338787349900
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 102,
                    "pathId": 148787247624701643
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8982375895227829883,
            "blockIdx": 18
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "こうして、ステイゴールドの姿を探しに\n来たが……結局、彼女は見つからなかった。",
            "enText": "Just like this, I went searching for Stay \nGold. I made my way here but… she \nwas nowhere to be found.",
            "nextBlock": 20,
            "origClipLength": 95,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "pathId": -8406455780681528138,
            "blockIdx": 19
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "おっ。なんだ……ちょうど帰りか？",
            "enText": "<i>Oh</i>. What's up… You heading back?",
            "nextBlock": 21,
            "origClipLength": 65,
            "voiceIdx": 80,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "ステゴ！どこにいたんだ？",
                    "enText": "Stego! Where were you?",
                    "nextBlock": 21
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "ステゴ！どこにいたの？",
                    "enText": "Stego! Where were you?",
                    "nextBlock": 21
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 46,
                    "pathId": 3501423866835280676
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 76,
                    "pathId": 7774823558226643271
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6194752493327162123,
            "blockIdx": 20
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "そりゃ、『あの場所』を観に行ってたのさ。\nメモ残しといたろ？",
            "enText": "Well, I was touring around \"that place\". \nDidn't I leave a note?",
            "nextBlock": 22,
            "origClipLength": 84,
            "voiceIdx": 0,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 91,
                    "pathId": -5410878648475855906
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 95,
                    "pathId": 3207549679120369183
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7779584888397913331,
            "blockIdx": 21
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "結局、最後までわからずじまいだった。\n『あの景色』とは何だったのだろう……。",
            "enText": "In the end, I still didn't find out where she \nwas. I wonder what \"that scenery\" could've \nbeen……",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "origClipLength": 94,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 105,
                    "pathId": 6254597377977207206
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 105,
                    "pathId": 5967951623639972209
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2760021083188374605,
            "blockIdx": 22
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "屋上に行くとステイゴールドは\n塔屋に腰を下ろして座っていた。",
            "enText": "Reaching the rooftop, I notice Stay Gold's \nlegs dangling from the rooftop structure \nas she sat up there slouching.",
            "nextBlock": 24,
            "origClipLength": 84,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "危ないよ！戻って！",
                    "enText": "Isn't that dangerous?! Come down!",
                    "nextBlock": 24
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6063204430633311045,
            "blockIdx": 23
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "まあそう目くじら立てるなって。\n絶壁の崖に座るよりはマシだろ？",
            "enText": "There's no need to sweat the small things. \nStill better than sitting on the edge of a \ncliff right?",
            "nextBlock": 25,
            "origClipLength": 85,
            "voiceIdx": 21,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "そ、それはそうだけど……！！",
                    "enText": "S-S-Sure, but…!",
                    "nextBlock": 25
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 71,
                    "pathId": 4940201942810289037
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 70,
                    "pathId": -5374422497847920925
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6012431573335832425,
            "blockIdx": 24
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "……ここの景色を目に焼き付けてるんだよ。",
            "enText": "…I'm burning this scenery into my memory —",
            "nextBlock": 26,
            "origClipLength": 71,
            "voiceIdx": 80,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 124,
                    "pathId": -8882153564477924910
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 72,
                    "pathId": -4844214305535966211
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 82,
                    "pathId": 6345502360181854321
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6874177938560473862,
            "blockIdx": 25
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "私はよく学園を離れるからさ。\nこっからの景色ってのは\n案外珍しい……そう思ってな。",
            "enText": "Since I don't come to the academy often. \nThis type of scenery… It's unexpectedly \nrare y'know.",
            "nextBlock": 27,
            "origClipLength": 98,
            "voiceIdx": 0,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "どう？学園からの景色は",
                    "enText": "How does the academy look then?",
                    "nextBlock": 27
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 4436286271782312727
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 109,
                    "pathId": -7931925699884675570
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 109,
                    "pathId": 9038262491095881409
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7314552168211628539,
            "blockIdx": 26
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "そりゃあ、悪くないよ。もちろん。",
            "enText": "Well of course, it's not bad at all.",
            "nextBlock": 28,
            "origClipLength": 65,
            "voiceIdx": 8,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 23,
                    "pathId": -2572722421778093023
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 76,
                    "pathId": 581247664516761763
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2672229491480733909,
            "blockIdx": 27
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "旅に出る前に焼き付けておくさ。\nここから見える色んなものをな。",
            "enText": "I want to commit all the different things I \ncan see in this place to my memory \nbefore I leave for another journey.",
            "nextBlock": 29,
            "origClipLength": 85,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 124,
                    "pathId": -389621136788894357
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 96,
                    "pathId": 3834611845513929659
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 96,
                    "pathId": 314326308295284215
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 761162384049093040,
            "blockIdx": 28
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "あんたも少し眺めていけよ。\n普段は見過ごしている何かが、\n見つかるかもしれないぞ？",
            "enText": "You should take a closer look as well. It \nmay be the same scenery you see everyday, \nbut I reckon you could find something new.",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "origClipLength": 98,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
